      "content": "that's fair. i guess i'm also wondering about the equity part you mentioned earlier. some people are saying it's basically just a regressive tax that punishes working people who can't afford the fee, while others say it's actually progressive because the money goes to public transit. in your experience as a consultant, which side of that argument is actually more grounded in reality?",
